extends layout

block content
  section.page-hero
    p.eyebrow About us
    h1 We make mystery shopping fun, simple, and themed.
    p Mystery Crate Co. is a fake class-project company that sells curated mystery boxes for hobbies, gifts, and surprise unboxings.
  section.section.about-grid
    .summary-card
      h2 Our mission
      p We help customers choose a theme they already love, then enjoy the surprise of discovering what is inside the box.
      p This website is a student e-commerce demo built with Node.js, Express, SQLite, Pug, CSS, and browser JavaScript.
    .summary-card
      h2 What makes us different
      ul.contents-list
        li 12 unique products with images, prices, descriptions, and stock
        li Search and filtering by product name, theme, description, and keyword
        li Mock checkout that stores orders in SQLite
        li Account pages with login, registration, and purchase history
    .summary-card
      h2 Class project note
      p This site does not sell real products or process real payment information. Checkout is only a mock payment flow for the project.
